    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's not really true though. the people in these cafes? they're just strangers. and my \"people\" back home... i haven't spoken to them in months. it feels like if I just stopped existing, the world would just keep spinning exactly the same way. like im just a glitch that finally got fixed.",
