      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so heavy sometimes. like there's no point in trying to \"be part of the fabric\" if the fabric doesn't even care i'm here. everything is just so loud and exhausting. i wonder if there's actually just peace in finally letting go and not having to fight to be seen anymore. i dont know. i just feel so tired of being a glitch.",
